text: I have been asked before of my ferrets are a dog, a cat, a stoat, a pine marten, a weasel....
On the bus, caught a glimpse of a guy walking a small furry creature on a leash. Not a dog or cat. WTH was that?? A ferret? Stoat?....
When I post about pets, I seem to gain followers. Let's test this...cat kitten dog puppy bird ferret stoat weasel gerbil giant ninja squid.
